{"tid":677482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓政客怒斥中國人是賤畜    官方機構：沒問題","createTime":"2018-05-25T08:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T15:27:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":227,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b2a771483786c1fabfc63b2ae60acfee3dea55","tid":677482,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"南韓前國會議員車明進（차명진），去年12月在《MBN》新聞節目上談到總統文在寅訪中的態度時，怒斥「難道要我們向『賤畜（떼놈，蔑稱中國人的用詞）』俯首稱臣嗎？」此段評論經過官方機構審議後，認為並無問題。<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《今日媒體》報導，大韓民國廣播通訊委員會（KCC，相當於台灣NCC），於4月開會討論是否要針對車明進的用詞向該電視台進行懲處。KCC大多數成員認為有必要對此警告，畢竟這種貶義的言論，也影響了在南韓生活的中國人，傳達出不尊重文化多樣性和種族歧視的態度。<br />\n<br />\n不過與會委員也一致認為，當時主持人立刻阻止發言的前議員，車明進也馬上道歉，所以基本上是沒有什麼問題。對於KCC的結論，南韓公民聯盟於5月23日晚間7時舉行新聞廣播標準公聽會，認為電視台仍需受到懲罰，並呼籲官方展開行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2437130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2437130&d=YbuBPTZzxgtB6n4KcdqCx0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d70f6af7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2437130&h=10b6f375\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2437130</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eaf82b571144a1fe1be0ac0370e7e6270b0bb16","tid":677482,"uid":58552,"like":46,"dislike":5,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"泡同支都係一擔擔"},{"pid":"a73ab92976c466d312ad7e5ec9f1e114fd38f4c9","tid":677482,"uid":4783,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:41:47.000Z","msg":"鬧完你狗賤種<br />\n<br />\n我就鬧係你狗賤種既言論道歉，請原諒我稱呼你做狗賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dc3b1b1a58ec8078685231c1f039fe74183949"